# Node. Project Rules

## Design Philosophy

- Botanical Archive
- Quiet Luxury
- Observation First
- Photo-centric UI
- Dark UI

## SwiftUI Rules

- Prefer small composable views
- Use MVVM
- Avoid massive View files
- Async/await first
- Local-first architecture

## UX Principles

- Never block observation flow
- No loading interruptions
- Fast camera flow
- Silent transitions

## Architecture

- SwiftUI
- SwiftData
- Supabase
- Cloudflare R2

## Code Style

- Feature-based folders
- Reusable components
- Minimal business logic in View